  <odd audience="internal" id="aspace_981a263149303fc2f06e22a3ab6ba4e9">
    <head>General Note</head>
<p>Some 1952 and 1958 schedules were located in the 1966 file, apparently when they were used for comparative studies.</p>  </odd>
  <scopecontent audience="internal" id="aspace_304a7910380d69df44ca9fa2aa351c84">
    <head>Scope and content</head>
<p>Survey records on rural living, compiled in the Dumaguete area, Leyte, Philippines, 1952, 1958, and 1966.  Also, code books, maps, analyses, publications.  Robert A. Polson directed the project.</p>  </scopecontent>
  <prefercite audience="internal" id="aspace_1e636cf322e0fe174a3eb5656cb246b8">
